12
00:01:48,030 --> 00:01:49,910
I just hope it won’t happen to us.

13
00:01:56,500 --> 00:01:59,030
[The woman accuses Yang Weida of sexual harassment used to be sponsored by Weida Fund.]

14
00:02:00,270 --> 00:02:02,390
Look. There is more news about the sexual harassment case

15
00:02:02,390 --> 00:02:03,510
involving the boss of Weida Group.

16
00:02:03,510 --> 00:02:04,110
More news?

17
00:02:04,110 --> 00:02:04,870
The truth is nothing like that.

18
00:02:04,870 --> 00:02:07,110
Just when you think you know someone, they surprise you.

19
00:02:07,110 --> 00:02:09,570
There are all sorts of villains in the world.

20
00:02:11,190 --> 00:02:13,510
This woman is so ungrateful. Oh my god!

21
00:02:24,070 --> 00:02:24,990
What a shame!

22
00:02:25,590 --> 00:02:26,590
This is huge. Check it out!

23
00:02:26,590 --> 00:02:27,590
The founder of Weida Group, Yang Weida,

24
00:02:27,590 --> 00:02:28,820
