25
00:02:28,820 --> 00:02:31,020
How come I didn't see that piece of news?

26
00:02:32,020 --> 00:02:32,829
What a shock!

27
00:02:32,829 --> 00:02:35,120
Guo Yu and I were both poor back then.

28
00:02:35,190 --> 00:02:36,390
It wasn't easy for us.

29
