more than I do.

32
00:02:41,900 --> 00:02:43,620
She takes a special liking

33
00:02:43,650 --> 00:02:45,130
for fashionable stuff.

34
00:02:45,150 --> 00:02:50,500
[Weida Group]

35
00:02:45,390 --> 00:02:47,230
So she might spend a bit more than others.

36
00:02:47,230 --> 00:02:49,270
We found it enviable

37
00:02:49,410 --> 00:02:50,990
that she was employed by Weida Group.

38
00:02:50,990 --> 00:02:53,040
But she thought

39
00:02:53,070 --> 00:02:55,310
her paycheck wasn't big enough.

40
00:02:59,070 --> 00:02:59,829
Look at this girl.

41
00:02:59,829 --> 00:03:02,030
She shouldn't make a profit from lying.

42
00:03:02,110 --> 00:03:02,990
Look!

43
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:05,670
Mr. Yang.

44
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:06,880
Make way there!

45
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:08,850
Mr. Yang!

46
00:03:11,430 --> 00:03:12,830
Make way! Thank you.

47
00:03:12,830 --> 00:03:13,550
Excuse me.

48
00:03:14,510 --> 00:03:16,510
Please be quiet. Quiet!

49
00:03:17,110 --> 00:03:18,950
What has happened

50
00:03:18,950 --> 00:03:21,150
is deeply harrowing my client's heart.

51
00:03:21,230 --> 00:03:23,710
Meanwhile, we appeal to all media friends

52
00:03:23,730 --> 00:03:26,090
to stop harassing Guo Yu,

53
00:03:26,230 --> 00:03:27,690
and to give her more space.

54
00:03:27,790 --> 00:03:28,920
We have faith in law,

55
00:03:29,100 --> 00:03:32,270
justice and human conscience. Thank you!

56
00:03:32,550 --> 00:03:33,820
Alright, alright.

57
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:41,010
Let's go.

58
00:03:42,710 --> 00:03:44,680
Ms. Guo, were you really sexually harassed?

59
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,670
Can you tell us in more detail?

60
00:03:45,670 --> 00:03:46,150
Ms. Guo,

61
00:03:46,170 --> 00:03:48,240
it's said that Weida Fund helped you through college.

62
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,170
Is that correct?

63
00:03:49,870 --> 00:03:50,600
Go after her!

64
00:03:51,570 --> 00:03:53,320
The group understands the hardship

65
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:55,770
[Weida Group Press Conference]

66
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:55,990
that Ms. Guo Yu has experienced after being dismissed.

67
00:03:55,990 --> 00:03:58,320
The group also expresses regret and shock

68
00:03:58,390 --> 00:04:00,500
about Ms. Guo Yu's allegations.

69
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:02,390
It is the group's belief that the court

70
00:04:02,390 --> 00:04:04,840
will respect and restore the truth

71
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:08,320
to serve justice and clear Mr. Yang Weida's name.

72
00:04:08,990 --> 00:04:11,390
Now, let's give the floor to Mr. Yang Weida,

73
00:04:11,390 --> 00:04:13,470
president of Weida Group.

74
00:04:15,710 --> 00:04:17,570
Everything happened out of blue.

75
00:04:18,300 --> 00:04:19,899
The case caught me off guard.

76
00:04:20,930 --> 00:04:21,810
To be honest,

77
00:04:24,270 --> 00:04:25,350
my heart aches.

78
00:04:27,420 --> 00:04:28,740
At this moment,

79
00:04:29,790 --> 00:04:30,830
I'm sad.

80
00:04:32,710 --> 00:04:33,350
I...

81
00:04:59,580 --> 00:05:01,350
I'd like to speak on Mr. Yang's behalf.

82
00:05:01,350 --> 00:05:02,670
Ms. Guo Yu used to receive financial support

83
00:05:02,670 --> 00:05:04,710
from Weida Group.

84
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:07,060
I guess you all know about that.

85
00:05:07,910 --> 00:05:09,590
Since the establishment of Weida Fund,

86
00:05:09,590 --> 00:05:10,530
over these years,

87
00:05:10,530 --> 00:05:12,590
how many students have we sponsored?

88
00:05:13,050 --> 00:05:15,170
We have helped more than 70 students

89
00:05:15,790 --> 00:05:17,470
get admitted to colleges,

90
00:05:17,910 --> 00:05:19,440
and start their college life.

91
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:21,880
Now, over 40 students

92
00:05:21,900 --> 00:05:23,460
have finished their study.

93
00:05:24,150 --> 00:05:25,480
I'm very happy for them.

94
00:05:28,470 --> 00:05:29,860
I know my husband well.

95
00:05:30,590 --> 00:05:33,390
I'm familiar with his personality and integrity.

96
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:35,150
I trust him.

97
00:05:38,110 --> 00:05:39,670
I also know Ms. Guo Yu well.

98
00:05:40,110 --> 00:05:41,230
But today,

99
00:05:41,270 --> 00:05:42,870
I won't say much about her.

100
00:05:43,710 --> 00:05:45,670
I just want to clarify one thing.

101
00:05:47,710 --> 00:05:49,150
I was responsible for

102
00:05:50,350 --> 00:05:51,990
assessing

103
00:05:52,390 --> 00:05:53,710
Ms. Guo Yu's work performance.

104
00:05:53,710 --> 00:05:54,710
It was my decision

105
00:05:55,140 --> 00:05:56,180
to dismiss her.

106
00:05:56,670 --> 00:05:59,130
We'd provide support for students' growth,

107
00:05:59,470 --> 00:06:00,670
but we would never

108
00:06:01,750 --> 00:06:03,280
be a meal ticket for anyone.

109
00:06:09,050 --> 00:06:10,570
You ungrateful brat!

110
00:06:10,710 --> 00:06:12,410
How can you sue someone you owe a favor to?

111
00:06:12,410 --> 00:06:13,770
Where are you morals?

112
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,390
Do you even have a conscience?

113
00:06:15,390 --> 00:06:16,450
Sooner or later...

114
00:06:16,780 --> 00:06:17,930
Let me see what's written here.

115
00:06:17,930 --> 00:06:20,190
Look. Everything's turned upside down.

116
00:06:23,030 --> 00:06:23,790
Gosh!

117
00:06:24,350 --> 00:06:25,230
Look.

118
00:06:26,230 --> 00:06:27,580
This is beyond my imagination.

119
00:06:27,580 --> 00:06:29,180
Guo Yu is rather plain looking.

120
00:06:29,180 --> 00:06:31,390
Why would something like this happen to her?

121
00:06:31,390 --> 00:06:33,630
I heard that Mr. Yang's wife

122
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:35,070
is gorgeous.

123
00:06:35,110 --> 00:06:36,470
Oh. Really?

124
00:06:36,470 --> 00:06:37,030
Yes.

125
00:06:37,230 --> 00:06:38,060
Are you referring to her?

126
00:06:38,060 --> 00:06:38,860
Isn't this...

127
00:06:39,630 --> 00:06:40,730
How could she do this?

128
00:06:40,730 --> 00:06:41,620
Welcome back!

129
00:06:49,060 --> 00:06:50,420
She is so ungrateful.

130
00:07:10,420 --> 00:07:12,880
We'd provide support for students' growth,

131
00:07:13,230 --> 00:07:14,440
but we would never

132
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:17,050
be a meal ticket for anyone.

133
00:07:17,270 --> 00:07:19,030
This incident won't stop us

134
00:07:20,110 --> 00:07:22,710
from sponsoring students in poverty.

135
00:07:23,710 --> 00:07:24,640
On the contrary,

136
00:07:25,590 --> 00:07:28,790
we will expand the coverage of sponsorship

137
00:07:28,910 --> 00:07:30,350
and increase the amount of fund receivers.

138
00:07:30,350 --> 00:07:33,110
The number will go up to 100.

139
00:07:45,540 --> 00:07:47,300
Guo Yu, open the door!

140
00:07:47,909 --> 00:07:49,710
Guo Yu, why is someone knocking at the door?

141
00:07:49,710 --> 00:07:51,030
Guo Yu, open up!

142
00:07:51,030 --> 00:07:52,830
Someone broke our glass window!

143
00:07:53,100 --> 00:07:53,700
Guo Yu!

144
00:07:53,700 --> 00:07:54,900
Come out and explain!

145
00:07:56,590 --> 00:07:57,830
Come out!

146
00:07:58,620 --> 00:07:59,300
Guo Yu!

147
00:08:03,990 --> 00:08:06,110
Weida Group was kind enough to ask people not to disturb her.

148
00:08:06,110 --> 00:08:07,150
Guo Yu is not worthy of sympathy.

149
00:08:07,150 --> 00:08:09,530
You never know how bad a person can be. Shame on her.

150
00:08:09,530 --> 00:08:10,670
I feel sorry for Mr. Yang.

151
00:08:10,670 --> 00:08:11,800
How disappointing!

152
00:08:12,250 --> 00:08:13,690
How could this happen?

153
00:08:14,150 --> 00:08:15,590
You were right.

154
00:08:16,110 --> 00:08:16,910
Look at these.

155
00:08:17,110 --> 00:08:18,170
Being poor doesn't give you privilege!

156
00:08:18,170 --> 00:08:19,610
The offender sues the offended.

157
00:08:19,610 --> 00:08:20,820
It's on the headlines.

158
00:08:20,820 --> 00:08:22,950
Someone must have hired cyber trolls.

159
00:08:22,950 --> 00:08:24,640
It must be Chen Shuo's idea.

160
00:08:25,630 --> 00:08:27,750
This looks bad. We need to hire some too.

161
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:29,680
Xia Shu, stop making things worse.

162
00:08:30,990 --> 00:08:31,630
Ms. Luo, Ms. Qiu.

163
00:08:31,630 --> 00:08:32,470
Here comes Ms. Guo.

164
00:08:32,470 --> 00:08:33,110
Guo Yu.

165
00:08:33,309 --> 00:08:34,350
Ms. Luo, Ms. Qiu.

166
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:36,280
Someone invaded my personal privacy online.

167
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:37,990
Information about my family, my phone number

168
00:08:37,990 --> 00:08:39,830
and my ID has all been revealed.

169
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:41,210
They even posted photos of me accepting help

170
00:08:41,210 --> 00:08:43,350
from the foundation when I started college.

171
00:08:43,350 --> 00:08:43,870
Today, I have received hundreds of

172
00:08:43,870 --> 00:08:45,680
text messages and phone calls.

173
00:08:45,710 --> 00:08:47,710
Everyone's accusing me of being ungrateful.

174
00:08:47,710 --> 00:08:49,710
Someone even broke my glass window.

175
00:08:50,350 --> 00:08:51,830
Turn off your phone.

176
00:08:53,110 --> 00:08:54,310
What should I do?

177
00:08:54,700 --> 00:08:56,350
We have reminded you

178
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:58,050
of getting fully prepared.

179
00:08:58,710 --> 00:09:00,430
If now you feel too stressed

180
00:09:00,430 --> 00:09:01,590
to handle this,

181
00:09:01,970 --> 00:09:03,970
it’s not too late to drop the charge.

182
00:09:03,990 --> 00:09:06,350
Now Guo Yu needs emotional support.

183
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:08,750
Guo Yu, don't fear them. Believe in yourself.

184
00:09:08,750 --> 00:09:09,350
Guo Yu.

185
00:09:09,700 --> 00:09:10,790
Ms. Qiu is right.

186
00:09:11,110 --> 00:09:12,590
If you want to keep the case going,

187
00:09:12,590 --> 00:09:14,320
you'll have to calm down first.

188
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:17,190
Just keep your phone off.

189
00:09:17,470 --> 00:09:18,830
Stay away from the negative information

190
00:09:18,830 --> 00:09:20,110
on the internet.

191
00:09:20,310 --> 00:09:20,990
Just let us, your lawyers,

192
00:09:20,990 --> 00:09:22,590
take over the rest.

193
00:09:23,070 --> 00:09:24,190
When you get home,

194
00:09:24,350 --> 00:09:26,580
lock up the door and take a shower.

195
00:09:26,710 --> 00:09:27,970
Have a good sleep, too.

196
00:09:27,970 --> 00:09:29,170
If possible,

197
00:09:29,350 --> 00:09:31,470
read some books and watch soap operas.

198
00:09:31,470 --> 00:09:33,950
Just be patient and see how the case goes.

199
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:34,720
Okay?

200
00:09:35,710 --> 00:09:37,750
Okay, I'll listen to you.

201
00:09:41,110 --> 00:09:42,870
This is an old phone of mine.

202
00:09:42,870 --> 00:09:43,870
I no longer use it.

203
00:09:44,110 --> 00:09:45,430
I've also got a new card in it.

204
00:09:45,430 --> 00:09:46,750
For now, you can use this phone.

205
00:09:46,750 --> 00:09:48,430
You should keep in touch with us

206
00:09:48,430 --> 00:09:49,560
on this phone.

207
00:09:49,950 --> 00:09:50,830
Thank you.

208
00:09:52,350 --> 00:09:53,720
I should probably get going.

209
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:54,770
I'll walk you out. Come on.

210
00:09:54,770 --> 00:09:55,430
No, thanks.

211
00:09:55,430 --> 00:09:57,830
You've been very bothered by my case.

212
00:09:58,090 --> 00:09:59,060
I can take care of myself.

213
00:09:59,060 --> 00:10:00,590
Go and have a good rest then.

214
00:10:08,420 --> 00:10:09,870
We can't just sit here and do nothing

215
00:10:09,870 --> 00:10:11,320
when people smear her.

216
00:10:11,380 --> 00:10:13,180
We've gotta protect our client.

217
00:10:16,060 --> 00:10:18,300
Our opponent has held a press conference.

218
00:10:18,300 --> 00:10:19,170
I think

219
00:10:19,340 --> 00:10:21,740
it's necessary for us to draft a statement.

220
00:10:26,750 --> 00:10:29,550
You didn't expect it to unravel like this, did you?

221
00:10:29,990 --> 00:10:30,990
We did.

222
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:34,440
We got ourselves prepared in the beginning.

223
00:10:34,750 --> 00:10:36,520
But we underestimated the number of people

224
00:10:36,520 --> 00:10:38,630
taking their side and abusing Guo Yu.

225
00:10:39,750 --> 00:10:40,720
Are you panicked?

226
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:41,590
No.

227
00:10:41,740 --> 00:10:42,910
We are wondering

228
00:10:43,430 --> 00:10:44,470
if we should

229
00:10:44,830 --> 00:10:46,490
start protecting our client.

230
00:10:46,940 --> 00:10:48,140
Of course you should.

231
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:53,430
Ms. Fang, is this statement okay?

232
00:10:53,430 --> 00:10:55,690
It's too formal.

233
00:10:58,430 --> 00:10:59,630
Write down what I say.

234
00:11:03,110 --> 00:11:04,430
You can lead with this:

235
00:11:05,410 --> 00:11:06,450
Ms. Guo,

236
00:11:06,640 --> 00:11:09,720
up to this day, is still deeply grateful

237
00:11:10,470 --> 00:11:13,250
for the support of Weida Fund.

238
00:11:13,870 --> 00:11:17,050
But she doesn't agree that the sponsorship

239
00:11:17,110 --> 00:11:18,870
gives the founder of Weida Fund

240
00:11:19,100 --> 00:11:22,120
the right to sexually offend her.

241
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:25,270
So, Ms. Guo

242
00:11:25,390 --> 00:11:28,790
will continue to use law as a weapon

243
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:32,990
to defend her legal rights.

244
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:37,380
Make sure it gets stamped by Tianli Law Firm.

245
00:11:37,380 --> 00:11:38,780
Send it out in their name.

246
00:11:39,050 --> 00:11:40,550
I'll go to Tianli Law Firm right away.

247
00:11:40,550 --> 00:11:42,480
There's one more reminder for you.

248
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:43,060
What is it?

249
00:11:43,060 --> 00:11:44,590
It's about your witnesses.

250
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:46,730
Try to prevent them from backing down.

251
00:11:47,070 --> 00:11:48,580
Before the trial,

252
00:11:48,870 --> 00:11:50,800
keep looking for other witnesses.

253
00:11:52,190 --> 00:11:54,230
My gut tells me

254
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:57,000
that there's some key evidence

255
00:11:57,230 --> 00:11:58,350
you haven't found.

256
00:12:11,980 --> 00:12:13,730
Why haven't the dynamics of public opinions changed yet?

257
00:12:13,730 --> 00:12:15,860
Am I having poor internet connection?

258
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:22,420
Why are these comments still around?

259
00:12:26,630 --> 00:12:28,180
What's wrong with these people?

260
00:12:28,180 --> 00:12:29,840
Does justice no longer exist?

261
00:12:29,990 --> 00:12:30,830
Xia Shu,

262
00:12:31,040 --> 00:12:32,570
can you stop making noises?

263
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:33,990
We've issued our statement,

264
00:12:33,990 --> 00:12:35,710
but it hasn't changed anything.

265
00:12:35,710 --> 00:12:37,970
It's like throwing a stone into an ocean.

266
00:12:38,110 --> 00:12:39,350
I told you so.

267
00:12:39,550 --> 00:12:41,160
Tianli Law Firm is too small.

268
00:12:41,190 --> 00:12:42,760
The statement issued in its name

269
00:12:42,760 --> 00:12:44,520
wouldn't attract any attention.

270
00:12:44,520 --> 00:12:46,750
We should've done it in our firm's name.

271
00:12:47,110 --> 00:12:48,480
It's just a patent case.

272
00:12:48,750 --> 00:12:49,710
Finding a bigger case than that

273
00:12:49,710 --> 00:12:51,070
is a piece of case.

274
00:12:51,350 --> 00:12:52,230
Xia Shu,

275
00:12:52,420 --> 00:12:53,900
can you stop saying that?

276
00:12:54,070 --> 00:12:55,270
At least, when you leave this room,

277
00:12:55,270 --> 00:12:57,150
don't say that in front of others.

278
00:12:57,260 --> 00:12:59,580
Doesn't it concern you that people would hate you?

279
00:12:59,580 --> 00:13:00,830
I brought a case to the firm.

280
00:13:00,830 --> 00:13:02,290
Everyone would benefit from it.

281
00:13:02,290 --> 00:13:03,550
Why would they hate me?

282
00:13:06,920 --> 00:13:07,790
If you're angry,

283
00:13:07,790 --> 00:13:10,000
