00:40:39,710 --> 00:40:40,770
Outside your home.

887
00:40:48,470 --> 00:40:50,080
How did you...

888
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:51,930
Why would you drive me home?

889
00:40:52,040 --> 00:40:54,360
You're too drunk to recall it, aren't you?

890
00:40:54,360 --> 00:40:56,020
