899
00:41:08,330 --> 00:41:10,290
I'll get off now.

900
00:41:13,670 --> 00:41:15,530
You can barely stand on your feet.

901
00:41:17,220 --> 00:41:18,280
I'll walk you home.

902
00:41:18,450 --> 00:41:19,030
No need to.

903
00:41:19,030 --> 00:41:21,290
