922
00:41:55,110 --> 00:41:57,260
I need to send your car key back, lady!

923
00:41:59,130 --> 00:42:00,200
Come with me.

924
00:42:07,490 --> 00:42:08,100
Here.

925
00:42:09,400 --> 00:42:12,140
Just leave the key here.

926
00:42:12,170 --> 00:42:13,330
Don't go upstairs.

927
00:42:13,990 --> 00:42:15,390
Don't follow me.

928
00:42:15,880 --> 00:42:16,760
